The Keiser Report (Russia Today) No. 95
- Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert -
Tuesday, 16 November 2010


[sebaygo1]


Markets! Finance! Silver! 

Max and Stacy look at the epic battle between debtors and creditors bringing out the kneepads, downgrades and last rites.

In the second half of the show Max talks to Michael Krieger -- head of the KAM LP fund and frequent contributor at ZeroHedge.com -- about a gold standard in the hands of the people.
